		<h2 class="comic-title">Wolverine: Origin</h2>
		
		<p>"Dog" is the son of a drunk farmhand who works for the wealthy Howlett family. He is friends of the heir to the Howlett fortune: James. Dog's Father beats him and tells him that they think that the are better than him. Eventually Dog's father is revealed to have had an affair with the Howlett boys mother and is actually James' father.</p>

		<p><b>OMG Moment:</b> Wolverine, the living weapon, is revealed to be the small sickly James Howlett when, in a fit of rage, he sinks little bone claws into His own father.</p>